text: Lilliana Junaedy (born 5 January 1996) is an Indonesian beauty model, winner of Miss International 2017. She is the first woman from Indonesia to hold this title. == Biography == Lilliana was born on 5 January 1996 in Bandung in a family of China and Indonesia origin. She has a younger brother Audi Danendra. On February 2, 2020, Lilliana married Oskar Mahendra. She has a daughter. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian people
